metadata.name: Onyema
metadata.description:
Onyema is a girl filled with questions and curiosity
Born into a world filled with longing thoughts 'Who Knowsâ€™, 
Against all odds, Would I triumph, 
Who knows what the future holds for me?'
She spent the early years of her life afraid of never fitting in. 
Afraid to try, Onyema watched life pass her by.

Looking for answers, unsure of possibilities,
In search of relief, She stumbles upon her past self
Aligned with her present, She comes to realize
Although there aren't certain answers to her questions
One thing remains Constant, Which is in fact HER

Who she is, a person, living, working, dreaming
Her Past, Present, and the Unknown
Her Values, and Her Knowledge

I am Onyema and with me comes these endless questions,
I've chosen to live in the moment 
No one has the answers to my questions except God.
Although it seems unclear, I haven't been more sure

I believe we are all Onyemas at a certain point in our lives
But I urge you in times of uncertainty Keep Trying.
